OL,5, A codeword used by police to give a    
OL,6, family access to a dying son in        
OL,7, hospital was racist, says his mother.  
OL,9,FSheldon Lewcock was hit by a van in    
OL,10,FTilehurst, Reading, in August 2022.    
OL,12,FThe 19-year-old, who was mixed race,   
OL,13,Fwas protected in hospital by police who
OL,14,Fgave his mother the codeword "banana"  
OL,15,Ffor when she wanted to visit.          
OL,17,FThames Valley Police said its          
OL,18,Fprofessional standard's department was 
OL,19,Finvestigating the use of the word.     
